    <Feat>
      <Name>Goodberry</Name>
      <Description>Transmutes natural matter around you into Goodberries.
Goodberries are infused with primal magic and provide a full meal's nourishment.
If eaten in a tavern, they act as tavern food and drink, refilling your health
and spell points. When cast, Goodberries appear in your inventory. The higher
the caster level, the more nourishing the Goodberries are.</Description>
