      </AutomaticAcquisition>
    </Feat>
    <Feat>
      <Name>Natural Fighting</Name>
      <Description>Natural Fighting grants you +4 Melee Power, Physical Resistance
and Doublestrike chance while in a druid animal form.
If in Bear/Dire Bear form, your Two-Handed ability mod increases by 25% and
+60/30/30% Strikethrough per time acquiring this feat.
